<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>RUAHCHANNAK LUNGPI CH320</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka ruahchannak a hram a fek, Jesuh Khrih thi lawng in a si, Ka bochan
 dang a um ti lo, Jesuh a min lawng in ka tei.

[C1]
   Lungfek in Jesuh ka bochan, A dang bochan awk a um lo, A dang bochan
   awk a um lo.

[V2]
 A mithmai ceu mui nih a phenh, A zaangfahnak kaa bochan lai, Thlichia
 hrang tilet tho hmanhseh, Ka hngatchannak Bawipa a si.

[C2]
   Lungfek in Jesuh ka bochan, A dang bochan awk a um lo, A dang bochan
   awk a um lo.

[V3]
 A biakam bangin a thi cang, Phannak kip ah kaa bochan lai, Ka velchum
 vial a rawh tikah Ka bochannak Jesuh Bawipa.

[C3]
   Lungfek in Jesuh ka bochan, A dang bochan awk a um lo, A dang bochan
   awk a um lo.

[V4]
 Muko thawng he a tum tikah, A hmaika ah ka dir te lai; A dinnak in kaa
 thuamh tikah, Sualnak loin ka um te lai.

[C4]
   Lungfek in Jesuh ka bochan, A dang bochan awk a um lo, A dang bochan
   awk a um lo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>320</hymn_number>
</song>